service: my-service

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.10
  iamRoleStatements:
    - Effect: "Allow"
      Action:
        - "s3:*"
      Resource:
        - "arn:aws:s3:::video-frames-bucket"
        - "arn:aws:s3:::video-frame-bucket/*"

functions:
  s3TriggerFunction:
    handler: handler.lambda_handler
    events:
      - s3:
          bucket: your-bucket-name
          event: s3:ObjectCreated:*
          rules:
            - suffix: .png

plugins:
  - serverless-python-requirements

custom:
  pythonRequirements:
    dockerizePip: true
